msgstr "At the top of the page, there are two panels. On the left is the original Class Under Test (CUT), and on the right there is a panel to write a new test, along with a \"Defend\" button which submits the test."

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:49
msgid "On the CUT panel, we can see the coverage of existing tests (in green) and the location of existing mutants (the symbols at the side)."
msgstr "On the CUT panel, we can see the coverage of existing tests (in green) and the location of existing mutants (the symbols at the side)."

