msgstr "Attack result showing that the mutant survived existing tests."

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:158
msgid "Equivalents"
msgstr "Equivalents"

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:159
msgid "It is possible to create a mutant which is identical in functionality to the CUT, so no test can pass on the CUT and fail on the mutated class."
msgstr "It is possible to create a mutant which is identical in functionality to the CUT, so no test can pass on the CUT and fail on the mutated class."

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:160
msgid "For example, the following functions are identical in behaviour, they are equivalent:"
msgstr "For example, the following functions are identical in behaviour, they are equivalent:"

