msgstr "Scoring System"

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:191
msgid "Mutants"
msgstr "Mutants"

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:192
msgid "For every test a mutant passes where the test executes the mutated line, the mutant gains a point."
msgstr "For every test a mutant passes where the test executes the mutated line, the mutant gains a point."

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:193
msgid "Mutants also gain one point for being created and surviving."
msgstr "Mutants also gain one point for being created and surviving."

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:195
msgid "Tests"
msgstr "Tests"

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:196
msgid "For every mutant a test kills, the test gains points equal to the score of the mutant."
msgstr "For every mutant a test kills, the test gains points equal to the score of the mutant."

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:197
msgid "A test gains a point for killing a previously untouched mutant."
msgstr "A test gains a point for killing a previously untouched mutant."

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:198
msgid "A test is also given an additional point for killing a newly created mutant."
msgstr "A test is also given an additional point for killing a newly created mutant."

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:200
msgid "Equivalences"
msgstr "Equivalences"

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:201
msgid "If an Attacker proves a mutant is not equivalent, they keep the mutant\'s points and gain an additional point."
msgstr "If an Attacker proves a mutant is not equivalent, they keep the mutant\'s points and gain an additional point."

#: src/main/webapp/jsp/help.jsp:202
msgid "If the Attacker accepts the mutant is equivalent, or the game expires, they lose the points of that mutant, and the Defender who claimed that it is equivalent gains a point."
msgstr "If the Attacker accepts the mutant is equivalent, or the game expires, they lose the points of that mutant, and the Defender who claimed that it is equivalent gains a point."

